org.threadly.concurrent.collections

Class ConcurrentArrayList.DataSet<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.threadly.concurrent.collections.ConcurrentArrayList.DataSet<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of object that is held
    Enclosing class:
    ConcurrentArrayList<T>

    protected static class ConcurrentArrayList.DataSet<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    This is designed to be an immutable version of the list. Modifiable actions will return a new instance that is based off this one. Because the array may change in areas outside of the scope of this dataArray, it is expected that the modificationLock is held while any modifiable operations are happening.
